OL,3,CManchester among first cities to get
OL,4,Cnew youth hubs
OL,6,FManchester is set to be one of the
OL,7,Ffirst cities in England to welcome a
OL,8,Fnew wave of "Young Futures Hubs"
OL,9,Fdesigned to provide support for
OL,10,Fteenagers' careers and mental health.
OL,12,FThe city has been named alongside
OL,13,Fseven other locations - including
OL,14,FLeeds, Birmingham, and Tower Hamlets -
OL,15,Fto pilot the centres for young people
OL,16,Faged up to 18.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
