CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775469930
OL,3,CManchester among first cities to get
OL,4,Cnew youth hubs
OL,6,FThe hubs are part of the Government's
OL,7,Fstrategy to prevent vulnerable young
OL,8,Fpeople turning to violence and crime,
OL,9,Fspecifically targeting areas with high
OL,10,Frates of anti-social behaviour.
OL,12,FThe rollout follows the closure of
OL,13,Fmore than 1,000 youth centres across
OL,14,Fthe country since 2010.
OL,16,F"The closure of over a thousand youth
OL,17,Fcentres didn't just take away
OL,18,Ffacilities, it took away community,
OL,19,Fconnection and opportunity for a
OL,20,Fgeneration," Culture Secretary Lisa
OL,21,FNandy said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775469930
OL,3,CManchester among first cities to get
OL,4,Cnew youth hubs
OL,6,F"We are determined to rebuild that.
OL,7,FWhat makes these hubs different is
OL,8,Fthat we're joining things up `
OL,9,Fwellbeing support, crime prevention,
OL,10,Fwork coaches, and youth services, all
OL,11,Fin one place."
OL,13,FThe services will also be available to
OL,14,Fyoung people with special educational
OL,15,Fneeds and disabilities (SEND) up to
OL,16,Fthe age of 25.
OL,18,FThe initial eight locations include:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
