FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775469930
OL,3,CManchester among first cities to get
OL,4,Cnew youth hubs
OL,6,FThese first hubs are part of a wider
OL,7,Fcommitment to open 50 centres across
OL,8,Fthe country.
OL,10,FThe initiative arrives as the
OL,11,FGovernment prepares to launch a major
OL,12,Fcrackdown on knife crime this week.
OL,13,FTitled Protecting Lives, Building
OL,14,FHope, the 10-year plan aims to halve
OL,15,Fknife crime within a decade.
OL,17,FPolicing Minister Sarah Jones
OL,18,Femphasised that the hubs are a crucial
OL,19,Ftool in diverting young people away
OL,20,Ffrom violence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
