PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775469930
OL,3,CManchester among first cities to get
OL,4,Cnew youth hubs
OL,6,F"Knife crime devastates lives," she
OL,7,Fsaid. "Behind every statistic is a
OL,8,Fchild who didn't make it home, a
OL,9,Ffamily whose world has been shattered,
OL,10,Fand a community left with fear.
OL,12,F"We will roll out these hubs in crime
OL,13,Fhotspots to divert young people from
OL,14,Fviolence, cut crime and protect
OL,15,Fcommunities."
OL,17,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,18,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,19,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,20,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
